Consider - information skill
------------------------------------------------------------
Swashbucklers are able to consider an opponent with a fair
degree of accuracy.  Relative experience, weapon strength,
and physical ability will be determined, as well as relative
armor strength.  At higher guild level, ethical behavior may
be determined, and there is a chance that the monster's
weaknesses will be found.

GL:  1
SP:  5
command:  sconsider <target>
duration: instant
